---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = 'Joshua Tree Wedding Invitations & Save the Dates | Hummingbird Social Studio';
const description = 'Custom Joshua Tree wedding invitations and save the dates inspired by desert weddings, boho style, national park elopements, and California desert celebrations.';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Joshua Tree Wedding Invitations & Save the Dates</h1>

    <p>
      Custom wedding invitation suites inspired by Joshua Tree, desert landscapes,
      warm earth tones, boho wedding style, and California national park celebrations.
    </p>

    <p>
      Whether you are planning an intimate desert elopement, a modern boho wedding,
      or a full weekend celebration near Joshua Tree National Park, your invitations
      should feel personal, stylish, and connected to the place.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="content-section">
  <div class="container">

    <h2>Inspired by Joshua Tree Weddings</h2>

    <p>
      Joshua Tree weddings have a distinct look and feel. The desert setting, golden light,
      rock formations, cactus details, and relaxed California energy all create a beautiful
      foundation for wedding stationery.
    </p>

    <p>
      Our Joshua Tree wedding invitations can be designed around your venue, color palette,
      wedding weekend plans, and overall aesthetic.
    </p>

    <h2>Popular Joshua Tree Wedding Invitation Styles</h2>

    <ul>
      <li>Joshua Tree wedding invitations</li>
      <li>Joshua Tree save the dates</li>
      <li>Desert wedding invitation suites</li>
      <li>Boho wedding invitations</li>
      <li>National park wedding invitations</li>
      <li>Minimalist desert wedding stationery</li>
      <li>Modern earthy wedding invitations</li>
      <li>California desert elopement invitations</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Designed for Desert Wedding Weekends</h2>

    <p>
      Many Joshua Tree weddings include more than just the ceremony. Couples often plan
      welcome parties, rehearsal dinners, group lodging, after parties, brunches,
      and weekend activities for guests.
    </p>

    <p>
      We can create cohesive wedding stationery for the full experience, including save
      the dates, invitations, RSVP cards, details cards, weekend itinerary cards,
      welcome signs, menus, seating charts, and day-of paper goods.
    </p>

    <h2>Custom Joshua Tree Wedding Stationery</h2>

    <p>
      Looking for something fully custom? We can design a wedding invitation suite that
      reflects your venue, your style, and the feeling of your Joshua Tree celebration.
    </p>

    <p>
      From simple and minimal to warm, boho, earthy, colorful, or artistic, each design
      can be customized to match your wedding vision.
    </p>

    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <h3>Do you design Joshua Tree save the dates?</h3>
    <p>
      Yes. We can create custom save the dates for Joshua Tree weddings, elopements,
      and destination wedding weekends.
    </p>

    <h3>Can the invitations include desert or national park-inspired details?</h3>
    <p>
      Yes. Design elements can include desert colors, natural textures, minimalist layouts,
      cactus details, mountain shapes, rock formations, or other Joshua Tree-inspired visuals.
    </p>

    <h3>Do you offer matching wedding day stationery?</h3>
    <p>
      Yes. Matching menus, welcome signs, seating charts, escort cards, and other day-of
      wedding stationery can be designed to match your invitation suite.
    </p>

    <h3>Do you offer printed and digital invitations?</h3>
    <p>
      We offer both digital invitation designs and professionally printed wedding stationery.
    </p>

  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
